== SOURCE

https://www.theverge.com/2016/3/23/11290200/tay-ai-chatbot-released-microsoft

== AGENT

Microsoft

== GOAL

Create an AI Chatbot

== DATA

Mined public data combined with input from editorial staff, including improvisational comedian.

== METHODS

Natural Language Processing

== RESULTS

While it did actually work in the beginning people began to exploit the system by teaching it inflammatory content. After many hurdles Tay was a failure and was moved onto a new chatbot called Zo. 

== ISSUES

Open to vulnrabilitys and inflammatory content to the public.

== SCORE

7

== COMMENTS

Understandably, that it went wrong considering it was mined data from the public and twitter. But ultimately the result will always be the same when training on public conversations and opinions.
